[11]	I want to raise a flag if there are certain questionable criteria for a planet

[12]	As Hanno (an admin), I want to see potential typos surrounded with an asterisk when manually reviewing

[13]		As Hanno (an admin), I want the tool to be able to match the same systems based on their descriptions even though they might have a different planet names in another catalogue

[14]		As Hanno (an admin), I want a notification on the desktop to appear when there is an update from another catalogue found

[15]		As Hanno (an admin), I want to be able to store and validate available updates offline and have them committed the next time I connect back to the internet

[16]		As Hanno (an admin), I want to be able to add sources of external catalogues for which my catalogue should get updates from

[17]		As Hanno (an admin), I want to be able to configure a template file of the data format for each source so that I can modify it if their data format changes later

